title: Nodes API
description: An API endpoint that returns a paginated list of `Node` objects.

title: Nodes file
description: A JSON Lines file containing one `Node` object per line. The file may be compressed using ZIP or GZIP.

title: Spans API
description: An API endpoint that returns a paginated list of `Span` objects.

title: Spans file
description: A JSON Lines file containing one `Span` object per line. The file may be compressed using ZIP or GZIP.
